nat.flybrains
  • Reference

Surface model of the VNCIS1 ventral nerve cord template brain

The VNCIS1 template is a shape-averaged, intersex template brain generated using the CMTK avg_adm tool.

References

Cachero S., Ostrovsky A.D., Yu J.Y., Dickson B.J., and Jefferis G.S.X.E. (2010). Sexual dimorphism in the fly brain. Curr Biol 20 (18), 1589-601. http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.cub.2010.07.045

Examples 

plot3d(VNCIS1.surf)
# slightly different display
plot3d(VNCIS1)
